			"styles": "\n\t/* the An+B `n` variable lowercases when it carries a numeric coefficient\n\t   (2N→2n), matching prettier. */\n\ta:nth-child(2n) {\n\t\tcolor: red;\n\t}\n\ta:nth-of-type(3n) {\n\t\tcolor: blue;\n\t}\n",
